-- Egypt central bank to hold exceptional forex auction on Monday
-- By Asma Alsharif
-- Mon Jan 27, 2014 03:04AM EST
-- None



CAIRO, Jan 27 (Reuters) - Egypt's central bank will hold an exceptional auction on Monday to sell $1.5 billion, it said in a statement.

The auction is significantly larger than the $40 million currency auction Egypt holds three times a week.